  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Fall of Dragonstone</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nVictory for the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/30px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/45px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/60px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aegon II Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/30px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/45px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/60px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Quince\" title=\"Robert Quince\">Robert Quince</a>†<br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aegon II Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/20px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/30px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/40px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a><br />Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alfred_Broome\" title=\"Alfred Broome\">Alfred Broome</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kingsguard.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">A few loyal members of the Dragonstone garrison<br />Baela on <a href=\"/index.php/Moondancer\" title=\"Moondancer\">Moondancer</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Black defectors<br />Aegon on <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Quince\" title=\"Robert Quince\">Robert Quince</a>†<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Moondancer\" title=\"Moondancer\">Moondancer</a>†<br />Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Minimal</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>fall of Dragonstone</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> occurred during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Dragonstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After escaping the <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Fall of King&#39;s Landing\">fall of King's Landing</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a> hid on <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone_(island)\" title=\"Dragonstone (island)\">Dragonstone</a>, the island stronghold of his rival, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a>. He convinced several <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a>, including Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alfred_Broome\" title=\"Alfred Broome\">Alfred Broome</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a>, to defect to the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> and help him take the island, with the assistance of <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tanglebeard\" title=\"Tom Tanglebeard\">Tom Tanglebeard</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Tangletongue\" title=\"Tom Tangletongue\">Tom Tangletongue</a>. Marston secured the <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a>, preventing Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> from sending a warning, while Alfred slew the castellan of Dragonstone, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Quince\" title=\"Robert Quince\">Robert Quince</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the coup, Aegon fought Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a>, both mounted on their dragons <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Moondancer\" title=\"Moondancer\">Moondancer</a>, respectively. The dragons fought in the pre-dawn sky above the castle, eventually slamming into the yard still fighting. Aegon jumped from the saddle twenty feet from the ground, but Baela crashed to the ground with Moondancer. Marston stopped Alfred from slaying the burned girl as she crawled away from her dying dragon, and Tom Tangletongue carried her to the maester.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Aegon II shattered his legs in a fall during the fight, but he refused <a href=\"/index.php/Milk_of_the_poppy\" title=\"Milk of the poppy\">milk of the poppy</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> offered it due to fear of Gerardys might poison him and because of his experience with it during his recovery after <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Battle at Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a>. Instead, Aegon ordered Gerardys to be fed to Sunfyre, though a part to remain to greet his sister.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Dragonstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> was now in the control of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a>, Aegon, and his <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a>, were seriously injured during the aerial duel over the island. The charred body of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Quince\" title=\"Robert Quince\">Robert Quince</a>, Dragonstone's steward, <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a>, captain of the guards, and the upper torso of Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> were hanged from the castle battlements near the gate to greet Aegon's sister when she arrived.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Rhaenyra eventually <a href=\"/index.php/Flight_to_Dragonstone\" title=\"Flight to Dragonstone\">returned to Dragonstone</a>, she and her followers were quickly defeated by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alfred_Broome\" title=\"Alfred Broome\">Alfred Broome</a>'s men.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fall_of_Dragonstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Template:Dance of the Dragons\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Dance_of_the_Dragons&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Dance of the Dragons (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Dance_of_the_Dragons&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129&#160;AC</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Coronation_of_Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Coronation of Aegon II Targaryen\">Coronation of Aegon II</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Coronation_of_R